        <div class="msgSubject">Awesome Lancer Solo Build</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-04 23:32:09   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-128893512950455521" id="quote-128893512950455521" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-128893512950455521" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=186&amp;mid=128893512950455521&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=128893512950455521&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_128893512950455521" onclick="followToggle('add','128893512950455521')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
