        <div class="msgUM"><a class="msgWhoName Scholar" href="/users/PuppetShow">PuppetShow</a><div class="msgWhoTitle Scholar">Scholar</div></div><div class="msgAvatar"></div><div class="msgStar"><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/s2.gif" alt="*"/></div><div class="msgWhoNum">94 posts</div>
