      <div class="msgContentFrame">So ive been messing around with classes, made a few posts on here and tried to get better info from you guys on what a good DD would be.  I am having a lot of fun on Lancer, im rank 15 physical level and rank 6 Lancer. <br /> <br />I leveled Conjurer to 8 so I could get shock spikes.  I am also using bloodbath from marauder, raging strike from archer, ferocity from lancer.  My skewer almost never misses and im fighting Marmots that con red to me.  I get about 158hp back from the Skewer. <br /> <br />Shock spikes basically owns!  The mob stays stunned 90% of the time and I hardly take any damage.  The damage I do take gets cleaned up by either a cure, second wind or my bloodbath buffed with skewer.  When you run out of MP switch to Conj hit tranquility then change back to lancer and you will have full MP on that class as well. <br /> <br /> <br />I didn't see this posted anywhere but just wanted to input that shock spikes make a huge difference in soloability.  Im just blowing thru mobs that con red.  When I hit 8 or 9 I will try some Dodo's. <br /> <br /> <br /> <br />Hopefully this was something new to add to the fun of lancer, so enjoy if it is! </div>
