      <div class="msgContentFrame">I see what your saying but bloodbath is a crappy skill I am sorry but it is true use cure instead. Shock spikes is a good skill for what your using it for so there probably isn't much issue with using now or later for that matter it wont destroy your Sp to the point that it breaks your grind but at the same time it really does get less useful over time. Lancer has the most balanced class skills period so looking out side the class for more than a heal is basically pointless the trend is now that a lot of DoW level lancer for invigorate and feint and if you get the guild marks fleet of foot. <br /> <br />As far as I see if you want to tank go glad if you want to might multiple mobs go MRD if you want to do insane damage go pug if you want to go broke go ranger and if you want the most balanced class out there go lancer.</div>
