      <div class="msgContentFrame">I never liked Ferocity. Sure, you get to try a big Bloodbathed hit or whatever, but you're spending so much time and stamina setting up a combo that often simply misses and flops unless you've got tons of extra TP or Feint. Even if everything works out, the payoff just isn't that good.  <br /> <br />As for Shock Spikes, I think the first thing anyone doing DoW/DoM should do is get CON to R8 for that because it improves your soloing power tremendously. You'll be able to solo leves much earlier and tackle tough mobs much more safely.</div>
