, Ferocity + Skewer II = 600% damage. I fail to see how this is not significant. That's 3 Feint mind you, but takes only 1.5 the time it takes for a Feint (Feint animation is twice as long as Ferocity, and as long as Skewer II - Skewer II and Feint have EXACTLY THE SAME animation). <br />3. Who said it is common to miss WS? All the test I saw about how DEX have no absolute effect on ACC (leaving it aside that SE did tell us DEX does affect ACC) clearly stated an average of 70% chance to hit. It isn't that bad.  <br />4. TP is never really a problem with Lancer with Invigorate and then Invigorate II, Full Thrust actually do MORE damage and give more TP gain than all other non TP move. People have accredited as much as 150% damage for Full Thrust, but I'm not sure about that. It does take more Stamina. <br />5. Like I said you can always use Ferocity with Feint, guarantee hit for 50% * 200% = 100% extra damage, an extra normal attack that guarantee hit in half the amount of time, not good? <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov 10th 2010  6:01pm by Khornette </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1807831.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /></div></div>
